# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================

# How this file works:
# 1. Patterns are matched from top to bottom
# 2. Last matching pattern takes precedence
# 3. When a PR is opened, GitHub automatically requests review from owners
# 4. Use @github-username or @org/team-name for ownership
# 5. Multiple owners can be specified: path/ @user1 @user2

# Solo project note:
# This file currently lists only @mbuckingham74 as the owner.
# When the project grows and new maintainers join, add them here:
#   Example: /frontend/ @mbuckingham74 @new-maintainer
#   Example: /docs/ @mbuckingham74 @documentation-team

